1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,936
"Hope" is the thing with feathers
希望 是个有羽毛的东西

2
00:00:04,560 --> 00:00:07,312
That perches in the soul
它栖息在灵魂里

3
00:00:08,016 --> 00:00:11,776
And sings the tune without the words
唱没有歌词的歌曲

4
00:00:12,304 --> 00:00:15,424
And never stops - at all
永远 不会停息

5
00:00:16,544 --> 00:00:21,520
And sweetest - in the Gale - is heard
在暴风中 听来 最美

6
00:00:21,936 --> 00:00:25,200
And sore must be the storm
令人痛心的是这样的风暴

7
00:00:25,888 --> 00:00:29,040
That could abash the little Bird
它甚至能窘困那温暖着

8
00:00:30,112 --> 00:00:32,448
That kept so many warm
多少人的小鸟

9
00:00:34,496 --> 00:00:36,704
I've heard it in the chillest land
我曾在最陌生的海上

10
00:00:37,504 --> 00:00:40,272
And on the strangest Sea
在最寒冷的陆地 听到

11
00:00:41,104 --> 00:00:44,496
Yet, never, in Extremity,
它却从不向我索取

12
00:00:45,520 --> 00:00:48,688
It asked a crumb - of me.
些微的 面包

